Here are some scripts to automate the H2 molecule binding curve on parsons lonsdale or kelvin.

The 3 commands to run are:


1. "./make_jobs.sh" # this sets up your calculations 
2. "sbatch gollum.sh" this runs your calculations 

# wait for the calculations to run ...
# then run:

3. "get_results.sh | xmgrace -" this plots the E vs d curve


